書（須附繕本）。 \r\n中　　華　　民　　國　　111 　年　　3 　　月　　9 　　日\r\n                                書記官  吳昕儒","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/SYEV/110%2c%e7%87%9f%e7%b0%a1%2c587%2c20220309%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"SYEV,110,營簡,587,20220309,1","JYEAR":"110","JCASE":"營簡","JNO":"587","JDATE":"20220309","JTITLE":"清償借款"}